Properties
Name
public string Name { get }
Location
public Path Location { get }

The path to the style.  If IsCSSOnly is set, this is the full Path to the CSS file.  If not, this is the full Path to the style's Style.txt.

IsCSSOnly
public bool IsCSSOnly { get }

Whether the style is simply a CSS file, like Blue.css, instead of a collection of files in a folder.

Inherits
public List<string> Inherits { get }

A list of style names this one inherits, or null if none.  Do not change.

OnLoad
public List<HTMLStyleOnLoadStatement> OnLoad { get }

A list of JavaScript OnLoad code statements associated with this style, or null if none.  Do not change.

Links
public List<HTMLStyleFileLink> Links { get }

A list of files to link to each output file, or null if none.  They can be .js, .json, or .css.  Each file is relative to Folder.  Do not change.

CSSFile
public Path CSSFile { get }

If IsCSSOnly is set, returns a path to the style's CSS file.  Will throw an exception if you attempt to read this variable when IsCSSOnly is not set.

ConfigFile
public Path ConfigFile { get }

If IsCSSOnly is not set, returns a path to the style's Style.txt configuration file.  Will throw an exception if you attempt to read this variable while IsCSSOnly is set.

Folder
public Path Folder { get }

If IsCSSOnly is not set, returns a path to the style's folder.  Will throw an exception if you attempt to read this variable while IsCSSOnly is set.

Variables
location
protected Path location

The path to the style.  If isCSSOnly is set, this is the full Path to the CSS file.  If not, this is the full Path to the style's Style.txt.

isCSSOnly
protected bool isCSSOnly

Whether location is a path to a CSS file or Style.txt.  This can be inferred from location itself, but it's checked so often that it's preferable to have a more efficient means of accessing it.

inherits
protected List<string> inherits

A list of style names this one inherits.  Null if none.

onLoad
protected List<HTMLStyleOnLoadStatement> onLoad

A list of OnLoad code statements associated with this style, or null if none.

links
protected List<HTMLStyleFileLink> links

A list of files to link to each output file, which can be CSS, JS, or JSON.  Null if none.

Static Variables
StyleExtensions
static public StringSet StyleExtensions

A StringSet of the supported extensions for files associated with styles.  This does not include image extensions; get those from Files.Manager.ImageExtensions instead.
